    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Residential substance abuse treatment patients who reside within the pre-specified
             catchment area who complete continuing care plans prior to discharge.

          -  Voluntary admit to residential treatment center; substance abuse or dependence; reside
             in targeted counties; and may be reached by telephone.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
